  "text": "changes to $attrs don't trigger options API watcher\n\n### Version\r\n3.1.4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://jsfiddle.net/Lg38t5qh/18/](https://jsfiddle.net/Lg38t5qh/18/)\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n* create component\r\n* watch $attrs\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n$attrs watcher is triggered on attributes change\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n$attrs watcher is not triggered\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
